Program: Outlook
Title: 26/10/2011
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00kwp3c
Last Broadcast Date: Thu 27 Oct 2011
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, Polina Zherebtsova tells Jo Fidgen about the diary she kept as a child during the Chechen war. Also, the story of Carmen Aguirre, whose family was part of the Chilean resistance to Pinochet. And French dentist Joe Bunni who risks his life to photograph polar bears. Show less